</taxonomicName>
(1), 
<taxonomicName id="4C654D6C9408FFD2BBC53D49FDDFF8F0" authorityName=", Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" box="[461,578,1859,1882]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="258" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="insitivus">
<emphasis id="B911EAFD9408FFD2BBC53D49FDDFF8F0" box="[461,578,1859,1882]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="258">M. insitivus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(2). 1a–b: habitus (PLT); 1c–e: median lobe of aedeagus in ventral (c), dorsal (d) and lateral (e) view [0.9 mm]; 1f: sclerites of endophallus [0.2 mm]; 1g: spermatheca [0.5 mm]; 1h: antenna [1.3 mm]. 2a–b: habitus (LT); 2c–e: median lobe of aedeagus in ventral (c), dorsal (d) and lateral (e) view [0.7 mm]; 2f: sclerites of endophallus [0.4 mm]; 2g: antenna [1.4 mm]. scI–IV: sclerites I–IV of endophallus; am: ampulla of spermatheca; dt: ductus of spermatheca; isr: ductus insertion on bursa copulatrix; vs: vasculum of spermatheca. Square brackets: length of scale segment.
</paragraph>
